thread.title_full: Otticanet recensione scritta da Larry Toole

author: Larry Toole
title: Larry Toole
text: I have to admit I was hesitant about ordering frames online, but when it's the only place to find the frames you are looking for you try it. I can say I am amazed at how quick my order was processed and delivered. Thank you very much and keep it up. You have my family's business from now on.
